name: Gimmick Puppet Terror Baby
desc: When this card is Normal Summoned: You can target 1 "Gimmick Puppet" monster in your GY, except "Gimmick Puppet Terror Baby"; Special Summon it in Defense Position. You can banish this card from your GY; this turn, your opponent cannot activate cards or effects in response to your "Gimmick Puppet" monsters' effect activations.
